name: "Bosque Azul"
description:
"The blue rain fell down, now I can see the neverending colors through the trees... long and tall and thin trees, a savage spirit is watching, to turn blue my path, I hope that around the corner is the Joy, the laugh and the Screams of the victory"

this is the 3rd of a series of acrylic paintings.

technique: Acrylic painting on paper.
measures: 88x31 cm.
2021.
